    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total stunner! This car is in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been babied since day one, always kept in the garage, and drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019m looking for a new home for it where it\u2019ll be just as loved. If you want a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, come take a look! I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you have!",
