    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies. This example is mechanically superlative; the dual-VANOS system has been bulletproofed, and the rod bearing recall is fully documented. The chassis is structurally sound with a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate common floor pan fatigue. Power is managed via a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with no bushing play or damper leakage. Finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather, the paint meter readings confirm original factory depth across all panels. A turn-key masterpiece for the purist collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
