    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This A80 chassis remains a benchmark of over-engineered Japanese performance. Power is derived from the iconic 2JZ-GTE 3.0L inline-six, featuring its original sequential twin-turbocharger configuration and factory-spec intercooler plumbing. The Getrag V160 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp, precise engagement, transferring torque through a pristine Torsen limited-slip differential. Every VIN tag is present on the original panels, and the undercarriage displays zero signs of oxidation or structural fatigue. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings, ensuring the double-wishbone setup delivers optimal lateral grip. Recent compression and leak-down tests confirm the internal health of the rotating assembly, with results well within factory tolerances. This is a collector-grade example for the discerning purist.",
